story_teamrocket_02_03000/2401_1201_0100:
What was up with that Togepi just now?
It Dynamaxed out of nowhere.
story_teamrocket_02_03000/2401_1201_0200:
And then it just scampered away right after we
took it down...
story_teamrocket_02_03000/2401_1201_0300:
Did you see how pained it looked right after it
approached us?
story_teamrocket_02_03000/2401_1201_0400: I’ve seen something like this before.
story_teamrocket_02_03000/2401_1201_0600:
Yeah. When Eternatus came to Pasio, it made a
lot of other Pokémon Dynamax all of a sudden.
story_teamrocket_02_03000/2401_1201_0700:
Everything was really chaotic because nobody
knew what was causing it!
story_teamrocket_02_03000/2401_1201_0800:
But didn’t Leon solve the problem by
catching Eternatus?
story_teamrocket_02_03000/2401_1201_0900:
Yeah, that’s what we thought. But if this is
happening again, something else must be wrong.
story_teamrocket_02_03000/2401_1201_1000:
That Togepi looked like it was having a
rough time.
story_teamrocket_02_03000/2401_1201_1100:
I think it was being forced to Dynamax even
though it didn’t want to.
story_teamrocket_02_03000/2401_1201_1200:
Hmm... Let’s go to Professor Bellis’s Lab and figure
out what to do next.
